---

## How to Run the App

1. Open R or RStudio.
2. Set your working directory to the project folder.
3. Install required packages if not yet installed:
   ```r
   install.packages(c("shiny", "shinydashboard", "DT", "here"))
   ```
4. Run the app:
   ```r
   shiny::runApp()
   ```

